Title: The Midges
Writer: Joseph Weisberg (created by), Tracey Scott Wilson
Actors: Keri Russell, Matthew Rhys, Brandon J. Dirden, Costa Ronin
Plot: Philip and Elizabeth tell Paige more about the family business, but pressing new questions arise when an operation takes a ghastly and unexpected turn. Meanwhile, a sensitive package jeopardizes Oleg's life back home.
